{"actor":"Jason Kuhrt","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T17:55:17Z","event_type":"updated","id":112,"issue_id":"kitz-78l","new_value":"{\"description\":\"`bd doctor` reports Dolt metadata modified immediately after `bd vc commit`, even with successful `bd dolt pull`/`bd dolt push` and healthy repo fingerprint. Determine expected behavior vs bug and normalize if possible.\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"kitz-78l\",\"title\":\"Investigate persistent metadata modified warning in kitz\",\"description\":\"\\nbd doctor v0.58.0  ──────────────────────────────────────────  ✓ 66 passed  ⚠ 3 warnings  ✖ 0 errors\\n\\nDATA \\u0026 CONFIG (9/10 passed)\\n  ⚠  Dolt Status: 1 uncommitted change(s)\\n      Changes: [metadata: modified ]\\n      └─ Run 'bd vc commit -m \\\"commit changes\\\"' to commit, or changes will auto-commit on next bd command\\n\\nGIT INTEGRATION (11/12 passed)\\n  ⚠  Git Working Tree: Uncommitted changes present\\n       M AGENTS.md                                                \\n M packages/cli/src/arg/arg.ts                              \\n M tools/tsgolint/bin/tsgolint                              \\n?? .claude/references/                                      \\n?? .claude/worktrees/                                       \\n?? debug.log                                                \\n?? docs/plans/no-unsafe-type-assertion-wave1-before-after.md\\n?? sketch.md                                                \\n      └─ Commit or stash changes, then follow AGENTS.md: git pull --rebase \\u0026\\u0026 git push\\n\\nMAINTENANCE (7/8 passed)\\n  ⚠  Dolt Locks: Uncommitted changes detected\\n      metadata: modified\\n      └─ Run 'bd vc commit -m \\\"commit changes\\\"' to commit, or changes will auto-commit on next bd command\\n\\nRun with --verbose to see all checks reports Dolt metadata modified immediately after , even with successful pull/push and healthy repo fingerprint. Determine expected behavior vs bug and normalize if possible.\",\"status\":\"ope